item.description:
HAPPY ANNIVERSARY TO "US!"


Come celebrate our One Year Anniversary with a Brunch at Clancy's Restaurant of Dennisport!

Relax and enjoy serene waterfront dining overlooking Swan River. Clancy's has become a local landmark striving to provide the complete Cape Cod dining experience.

The brunch menu includes Eggs Benedict, Crab Benny, Clancy's Corned Beef Hash & Poached Eggs
Chicken Oscar, Quiche Du Jour, Omelet Du Jour, and a Griddle Du Jour! Check out the brunch menu for yourself at http://clancysrestaur...

In addition to Brunch, the restaurant is also serves Soups, Salads, Burgers, Pasta, Sandwiches, and an exceptional Raw Bar in addition to many other selections!
